|cp|red|at|^*bOliverC:^*n|cp||at|  I mentioned that the system I teach does not follow "Classic" Precision in some respects. Here are the Opening Bids in the system I teach. 

The Openings up to and including 2@C are identical to the "Classic" Precision ones.

It is from 2@D upwards that some of them differ:
|Lg|e|at|^c@2
2@D ^d 16-23  with any 4441 shape.
